parakeet-sidecar
================

This component ports the Token-and-Duration Transducer (TDT) greedy decode
algorithm, the chunked-audio processing strategy, the ANE-aligned MLMultiArray
helpers, and the chunk token merger from:

  FluidInference/FluidAudio
  https://github.com/FluidInference/FluidAudio
  Copyright (c) FluidInference
  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

The relevant source files studied and ported were:
  Sources/FluidAudio/ASR/Parakeet/Decoder/TdtDecoderV3.swift
  Sources/FluidAudio/ASR/Parakeet/Decoder/TdtDecoderState.swift
  Sources/FluidAudio/ASR/Parakeet/Decoder/TdtConfig.swift
  Sources/FluidAudio/ASR/Parakeet/Decoder/EncoderFrameView.swift
  Sources/FluidAudio/ASR/Parakeet/ChunkProcessor.swift
  Sources/FluidAudio/ASR/Parakeet/AsrModels.swift
  Sources/FluidAudio/Shared/AsrChunkTokenMerger.swift
  Sources/FluidAudio/Shared/ANEMemoryUtils.swift
  Sources/FluidAudio/Shared/ASRConstants.swift

The code here is a reimplementation for Scribe's stdin/stdout line protocol;
FluidAudio is not bundled or linked as a dependency.

